### 7. Plasma Weapons

**Signature Rule:** ***Gets Hot*** + **AP 2**

**Identity:** Superheated plasma containment that can fry the user. The risk/reward tradeoff of Gets Hot is the defining plasma experience. AP 2 cuts through power armor and terminator plate.

| Weapon | Range | S | AP | Type | Notes |
| :---- | :---: | :---: | :---: | :---- | :---- |
| Plasma Pistol | 12" | 7 | 2 | Pistol, Gets Hot | Baseline. |
| Plasma Gun | 24" | 7 | 2 | Rapid Fire, Gets Hot | Baseline. |
| Plasma Cannon | 36" | 7 | 2 | Heavy 1, Blast, Gets Hot | Adds Blast at heavy tier. |
| Executioner Plasma Cannon | 36" | 7 | 2 | Heavy 3, Blast, Gets Hot | Multiple shots. |
| Tau Plasma Rifle | 24" | 6/7 | 2 | Rapid Fire / RF Gets Hot | Standard mode S6 safe; Overcharge S7 Gets Hot. |

**Baseline:** S7 AP2. Gets Hot is universal. Tau Plasma Rifles follow the convention via their Overcharge mode.

**Exception:** The Knight Plasma Executor (S9 AP2 Heavy 3, no Gets Hot) deliberately omits Gets Hot because the USR has no effect on vehicles per core rules. This is a documented vehicle exemption, not a family violation.

**Factions:** Imperium, Chaos, Tau (via Overcharge), Orks (Kustom Mega- weapons are plasma-adjacent but follow their own conventions with random Strength and Gets Hot).

---

### 8. Melta Weapons

**Signature Rule:** ***Melta*** USR + **S8 AP1**

**Identity:** Thermal fusion weapons that roll 2D6 for armor penetration at half range. Nothing survives a close-range melta shot. S8 AP1 is near-universal.

| Weapon | Range | S | AP | Type | Notes |
| :---- | :---: | :---: | :---: | :---- | :---- |
| Inferno Pistol | 6" | 8 | 1 | Pistol, Melta | Short-range sidearm. |
| Meltagun | 12" | 8 | 1 | Assault, Melta | Standard infantry melta. |
| Multi-Melta | 24" | 8 | 1 | Heavy 1, Melta | Longer range, heavier platform. |
| Melta Cannon | 24" | 8 | 1 | Heavy 1, Blast, Melta | Adds Blast. |
| Thermal Cannon (Knight) | 36" | 9 | 1 | Heavy 1, Large Blast, Melta | Knight-scale. S9 at superheavy tier. |
| Fusion Blaster (Tau) | 12" | 8 | 1 | Assault 1, Melta | Tau equivalent, identical baseline. |

**Baseline:** S8 AP1. Melta USR universal. Range scales with platform size (6" pistol → 12" assault → 24" heavy → 36" superheavy). Knight-scale weapons may increase to S9.

**Factions:** Imperium, Chaos, Tau (Fusion Blaster).

