**Identity:** Crystallized toxin shards. Wound based on toxic payload, not kinetic force. S1 or S— baseline — the shard itself does almost nothing; the toxin does the killing. Useless against vehicles (Poison has no effect on vehicles per core rules), which is intentional — Dark Eldar bring Darklight for armor.

