| Splinter Pistol | ~12" | 1 | 5 | Pistol, Poison (4+) | Baseline. |
| Splinter Rifle | ~24" | 1 | 5 | Rapid Fire, Poison (4+) | Standard Kabalite weapon. |
| Splinter Cannon | ~36" | 1 | 5 | Heavy/Assault, Poison (4+) | Volume of fire. |

**Factions:** Dark Eldar.

