### 25. Darklight Weapons (Dark Eldar)

**Signature Rule:** ***Lance***

**Identity:** Beams of concentrated dark matter that destabilize molecular bonds. High S, low AP, and Lance means even the heaviest armor offers limited protection. The premier anti-heavy-armor technology outside of melta.

| Weapon | Range | S | AP | Type | Notes |
| :---- | :---: | :---: | :---: | :---- | :---- |
| Blast Pistol | ~6" | 8 | 2 | Pistol, Lance | Short-range sidearm. |
