## RANGED WEAPON FAMILIES — ADMECH / MECHANICUS

### 35. Galvanic Weapons (AdMech)

**Signature Rule:** ***Rending***

**Identity:** Hyper-velocity solid rounds charged with electro-galvanic energy that disrupts biological processes. Precision weapons favored by Skitarii Rangers. The electrical charge occasionally causes catastrophic damage on a precise hit.

**Members:** Galvanic Rifle, Galvanic Caster. Stats TBD with Mechanicus codex.

**Factions:** Adeptus Mechanicus (Skitarii).

