### 36. Arc Weapons (AdMech)

**Signature Rule:** ***Haywire*** + ***Concussive***

**Identity:** Massive electrical discharges that overload machinery (Haywire — replaces armor pen vs vehicles with glancing/pen table) and stun living targets (Concussive — drop to Initiative 1). Dual-purpose weapons equally dangerous to vehicles and infantry.

**Members:** Arc Rifle, Arc Pistol, Arc Claw, Arc Lance. Stats TBD with Mechanicus codex.

**Factions:** Adeptus Mechanicus.

---

### 37. Transuranic Weapons (AdMech)

**Signature Rule:** ***Armorbane***

**Identity:** Ultra-dense, hyper-velocity rounds fired at extreme range. The projectile is so dense it punches through virtually anything. Armorbane (2D6 armor penetration) reflects the sheer kinetic energy of the round.

**Members:** Transuranic Arquebus, Transuranic Arrow. Stats TBD with Mechanicus codex.

**Factions:** Adeptus Mechanicus (Skitarii).

